data.meta_description: TBU-FULL - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document appears to contain scores and statistics from various soccer/football matches played around the world at different levels, including youth, reserve, and senior matches. The matches include teams from Europe, Asia, Africa, North America, South America, and Oceania. Scores range from 0-0 draws to 4-0 and 9-0 wins.
